Package org.ow2.chameleon.rose.introspect

Interface Summary
ExporterIntrospection This service provides minimal introspection about the service created by the exporter component providing this service.
ExportSupervisorIntrospection This service allows minimal introspection on the export-supervisor component.
RRegistryIntrospection This service provides minimal introspection about the EndpointDescription created by the local gateway which are published through the announcer providing this service.
